§7§oToss it in an ocean biome!

§fThe seas on Terra are definitely dangerous. It seems like the local fauna has made it difficult for alien invaders to take over the seas, yet, one of them seems to have no problem there...
Corallus belongs to the same faction as Smash, but they seem to behave independently of each other. The two share intelligence using amphybyite coves located on beaches, at the interface of the lands and seas they control.
